 Vao trang https://angular.io/guide/quickstart de xem huong dan cai dat.

1. Cai nmp
2. tao 1 folder va chay npm install -g @angular/cli de create angular project
3. run ng new my-app de tao 1 project angular moi. Luu y, cai ten project rat quan trong. hoi truoc tao bang cai ten
angular_sample thi bi loi path.name khi gio gi do, nhung ma khi doi ten thanh angularsample thi ko bi nua. Cai nay co
thoi gian thi tim hieu sau.

4. cd my-app
va run  ng serve --open de start server. (hoac ng serve --o)

dia chi mac dinh : http://localhost:4200/


5. Huong dan run bang Intellj idea

Trong intellj idea no co cai terminal. de cho tien thi ta can set up lai de co the chay command line truc tiep tu day.
